f" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Pre-Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(10/5/01 3:04:13 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Tablet</span><hr size=1> Oh, I guess I was not clear, the presentation is a maximum of 15 minutes, but I think it will go over 5 minutes.  Its going to consist of the explanation of the hardware, how it works, how it relates to the field of graphic design, why this specific tablet(Wacom Intuos2) is more accepted, Q&amp;A period, diagrams using handouts and powerpoint, and most important, the art of talking slowly<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
